{"tid":1734892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心臟同春袋都玩過，有無人諗過玩吓兩粒蛋蛋呢","createTime":"2019-11-18T12:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T12:30:21.000Z","uid":279625,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9a349ccea9b7071bdecee7bca2b9d0277db790e8","tid":1734892,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"如果中環係心臟，機場係春袋，咁我諗空運、海運就應該係兩粒蛋蛋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港唔止係國際金融中心，而且仲係國際運輸樞紐，而葵涌、青衣哩兩個地方就真係輸精管，如果大大力揸落去，會唔會飆眼水呢！？你自己諗啦！<br />\n<br />\n要考慮就係乜嘢方法，又快又難拆解！<br />\n<br />\n如果有架大貨車載木卡板，去到附近一路行一路跌，咁就大鑊啦，真係有排搞！<br />\n如果再有人混凝土加磚頭陣，真係死得人多，阿蛋蛋真係無得救！<br />\n<br />\n木卡板好易著火，頂都黑狗強攻，而且好多貨倉都係要俾搵人收當垃圾掉，非常易搵！"},{"pid":"3e846b1006ff25051f2e1d155eeb931928cc46cc","tid":1734892,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:20:49.000Z","msg":"1/20"},{"pid":"668c5b50a134a2417990027b727dc887c4589392","tid":1734892,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:21:03.000Z","msg":"2/20"},{"pid":"a0906158fbe1af4c144b40b9d2469c163ae04ddb","tid":1734892,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:21:13.000Z","msg":"3/20"},{"pid":"05e7f3d3ab3a31459f85c78d931952ed8d3d19e0","tid":1734892,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:21:23.000Z","msg":"4/20"},{"pid":"e8cc53a58cd28d3939a4d29bbb29d0c7b9848c9c","tid":1734892,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:21:37.000Z","msg":"5/20"},{"pid":"5bf33b14b22323de6b8734057e1e31239abc2852","tid":1734892,"uid":85906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:21:49.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"655ad67014ce0d99d109753bc012b4096547ac74","tid":1734892,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:21:56.000Z","msg":"6/20"},{"pid":